| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0243 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8e2bffb6-3dd0-5eaa-95b5-6e6cf50eb266"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
